SPEAKER   sd_test2 1 10.0  1.9 <NA>         <NA>         spkr1r <NA>
LEXEME    sd_test2 1 10.0  1.0 firstWord    lex          spkr1r <NA>
LEXEME    sd_test2 1 11.0  0.8 secondWord   lex          spkr1r <NA>

SPKR-INFO sd_test2 1 <NA> <NA> <NA>         adult_male     spkr2r <NA>
SU        sd_test2 1 11.9  2.1 <NA>         statement    spkr2r <NA>
SPEAKER   sd_test2 1 11.9  3.1 <NA>         <NA>         spkr2r <NA>
;; noscore zone should be 11.9 through 13.2
;; 11.9 is a SPEAKER boundary in the ref, and 13.2 is a word boundary
